{"tid":1322250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣海濱連儂牆被保安破壞","createTime":"2019-07-16T01:31:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T13:30:08.000Z","uid":229508,"like":32,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8136d935ec6f0eac17fd9eaed78a608d88d75e11","tid":1322250,"uid":229508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T01:31:11.000Z","msg":"啱啱放工返嚟，轉身過馬路之際，就見到海濱廣場門口有白衫保安起勢咁搣野，我即刻明，當我跑過去嘅時候個保安轉個頭就即刻返入去，雖然嗰度係私人地方，但係佢隨意咁破壞都係犯刑事法。<br />\n利申:都係啱啱先知海濱有連儂牆<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/myvtmSa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmyvtmSa.png&h=d86e62eb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C09JVcc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC09JVcc.png&h=2065220b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EEFdxYT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEEFdxYT.png&h=98cb3f35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n估唔到區區一個保安氣焰，同警犬一樣大，囂張跋扈！<br />\n唔係以為真係自己地方呀嘛門口狗？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你係咪有特權啦？你係咪大撚晒呀？</span>"},{"pid":"5fd692bdaf9cd07598b28575c0ab46805894ec43","tid":1322250,"uid":229508,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T01:33:42.000Z","msg":"見住佢破壞，自己又阻止唔到，真係有啲憤怒"},{"pid":"4a744abfbda8c68df5425a63e07cd6a6d8a9e6ba","tid":1322250,"uid":48947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T01:35:23.000Z","msg":"瞄住佢有冇蛇王吞bok<br />\n投訴"},{"pid":"a120d05f4360af1364834978c837fe9f1da7fe6b","tid":1322250,"uid":229508,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T01:35:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dCadx1r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdCadx1r.png&h=dc4e035c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事後搵唔到佢"},{"pid":"ea2043af1591cdd0c496abcef8f479e1f3c7a733","tid":1322250,"uid":229508,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4a744abfbda8c68df5425a63e07cd6a6d8a9e6ba","tid":1322250,"uid":48947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc